name: Stemn-Desktop
description: List of all Stemn Desktop versions. Find out more:

build:main.command: node -r babel-register ./node_modules/webpack/bin/webpack --config webpack.config.electron.js  --progress --profile --colors && cp app/package.json dist/

build:renderer.command: node -r babel-register ./node_modules/webpack/bin/webpack --config webpack.config.production.js --progress --profile --colors && cp -R app/renderer/assets dist/renderer

releases.name: v0.0.18
releases.body:
## Things we fixed
We hardcoded a dynamic IP into our app. We lost that IP lease. This one has a static IP.

releases.name: v0.0.19
releases.body:
### New Goodies
- Project task and commit changes sync in real time.
- Team members get added to your Google Drive or Dropbox folder when added to your project.


### Things we fixed
- Team members can now change the project folder. Fixes #10. Thanks @neil1993

releases.name: v0.0.17
releases.body:
### New Goodies
- Parent Assembly and Child Parts are now shown when a CAD file is previewed.
- Added date/time and 'toggle all' to to the Commit Preview.
- File changes now appear automatically.

### Things we fixed
- Camera sync between CAD files is now much smoother.

releases.name: v0.0.16
releases.body:
### New Goodies
- Added a **public indicator** to show if the project is public or private.
- Added a **file cache** that works for all files (including CAD renders) - all file previews are super fast - viewing a file you have already viewed takes just a couple of seconds - down from a minute!

### Things we fixed
- Fixed an issue ( #5 ) that meant Dropbox or Drive could not be auto-located if only one client was installed.
- Fixed #8 so camera only syncs between the right types of renderers. 
- Many other minor things.

releases.name: v0.0.15
releases.body:
### New goodies
- You can now **view revisions** for any file in your drive or dropbox - not just ones part of a project. Right click menu still only appears on Windows.
- Added support for **back and forward** mouse buttons.
- Added some **theme changes** - everything looks a bit nicer (my colleagues disagree).
- Added a **file list** view that shows all files related to a project.
- Added a **tutorial** explaining how to commit files.
- Added the **release notes** display on the Application Settings page.
- Added a toggle so **Auto-Update** can be turned off.
- Added a toggle so **Debug mode** can be turned on (this will log all actions in the console).
- Added a message to explain when/why a **revision has expired**.
- Added a circular **progress indicator** when images are uploaded.

### Things we fixed
- Fixed an issue where you could not upload a profile picture if you did not already have one.
- Fixed an issue caused by old google drive folders (with extra long Ids) related to #3 .
- Made some stuff run faster.

releases.name: v0.0.14
releases.body:
- Fixed issue #2 where users is logged out on a bad API request.
- Fixed an issue with revisions on the timeline.
- Added a Home button on the provider path select modal to partially address #3.

releases.name: v0.0.12
releases.body: - PDF files now supported in the file preview window

releases.name: v0.0.10
releases.body:
Added Code Signatures for Windows and Mac.
Mac Auto Update should work now!
